00:32:48,733 --> 00:32:49,859
Kapten.

557
00:32:52,445 --> 00:32:54,489
Ini untuk investigasi.

558
00:32:54,989 --> 00:32:56,074
Izinkan kami periksa.

559
00:33:01,788 --> 00:33:03,623
KESELAMATAN WARGA,
LINDUNGI PERDAMAIAN

